Command Sequence:
    flex sample*.lex
    gcc lex.yy.c -lfl
    ./a.out

Understand the input file
Format:
    definitions
    %%
    rules
    %%
    user code
The definitions section: "name definition"
The rules section: "pattern action"
The user code section: "yylex() routine"

Current Problems:
1. Identifiers are not being picked up correctly. It picks up reserved words as well. 
2. Comments are not being picked up correctly.
